title: Term Life. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2016)
description:
In theaters: April 8th, 2016

Description:

Everyone wants Nick (Vince Vaughn) dead. A desperate man, Nick takes out a life insurance policy on himself, payable to his estranged daughter (Hailee Steinfeld). But the policy doesn't take effect for 21 days and he might not live that long.

Director: Peter Billingsley

Writers: Andy Lieberman

Actors: Vince Vaughn, Hailee Steinfeld, Bill Paxton, Jordi Malla, Terrence Howard, Jon Favreau, William Levy, Mike Epps, Taraji P. Henson, Cain Velasquez

Genre: Action and Adventure, Thriller

Run Time: 1 hour 34 minutes
